              "free_text": [
                "The error in the determination of the cross",
                "section on oxygen is due to the uncertainty in the",
                "determination of the ratio of the areal densities of Au",
                "and O, and additionally due to count statistics of the",
                "oxygen peak and the background due to nuclear reactions",
                "with the carbon substrate."
              ]
