                    "date": 1988
                  }
                }
              },
              "free_text": [
                "",
                "For 7Li, there is good agreement with the data of",
                "rauhala and raisanen at energies below 5200 KeV. At",
                "higher energies, however, there is a disagreement by a",
                "factor of almost two, which is much larger than the",
                "error bars of the measurements.  The reason for this",
                "disagreement is not known.  The measurements were",
                "performed at slightly different scattering angles (165",
                "versus 170), but it seems unlikely that this small",
                "difference is able to explain this disagreement."
              ]
            }
